<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-that-case">in that case</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>既然如此；那样的话：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>—He didn’t want to talk to Sally.
他不想和萨利说话。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— In that case why did he agree to meet her?
既然那样，为什么他还同意和她见面？</p></div></div>